ing: 1 (12 fluid ounce) can club soda, or as needed
des: "Specialized beverage I created one evening at a friends party. After its success, I wrote it down in his Mr. BostonÂ®. It has been requested ever since."
ins:
Fill a cocktail glass halfway with club soda.
Combine rum and vodka in a cocktail shaker. Add ice, cover, and shake until chilled. Strain into cocktail glass with club soda. Garnish with a spritz of vermouth and orange peel.
